sections.content:
Functions use JSON schema to define their interface:

```json
{
  "name": "send_email",
  "description": "Send an email message",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "to": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Recipient email address"
      },
      "subject": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Email subject line"
      },
      "body": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Email message body"
      }
    },
    "required": ["to", "subject", "body"]
  }
}
```
